---
pagination:
  data: collections
  size: 1
  alias: tag
  filter:
  - all
  - feed
  - nav
  - page
  - post
  - postsLatest
  - tagList
  addAllPagesToCollections: true
renderData:
  title: Tagged "{{ tag}}"
  layout: {{ theme.tag.layout }}
permalink: /tags/{{ tag | slug }}/
---
{#
You Are Here:
- Tag
- src/site/page/tag.njk

How It Works:
- On build, this layout will generate 1 page for every Tag on the site
  as a postlist.

TODO:
